  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个HealthTech诊断引擎的事件处理流程。核心是从Aggregate产生事件开始，经过Event Store、Reactor，最后由Queue Worker执行副作用。我想确认一下参与者顺序：Aggregate、Event Store、Reactor、Queue、Queue Worker，还有Side Effect。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，六个参与者。我先搭建基础框架。Aggregate到Event Store是存储事件，然后Event Store通知Reactor，Reactor把任务推到Queue，Queue Worker取出来处理，最后触发Side Effect。这个流向对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对的。不过Side Effect执行完要有分支逻辑——成功的话标记任务完成，失败的话要重试。这部分用alt块来表现，Success和Failure两个分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Success",
        "Failure",
        "Retry Job",
        "Mark Job as Completed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上alt分支。成功路径：Side Effect返回Success给Queue Worker，然后Worker通知Queue标记完成。失败路径：返回Failure，然后触发Retry Job。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Return Success",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Return Failure",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "稍等，Reactor到Queue的那一步，我描述得不够准确。不是简单的\"通知\"，应该是\"Push Job\"，强调Reactor主动把任务推入队列。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Push Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，修正为\"Push Job\"。另外我检查了一下，Queue Worker到Side Effect的动作我标的是\"Execute\"，需要明确写成\"Execute Side Effect\"吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect",
        "Execute Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，\"Execute Side Effect\"更准确。还有Event Store到Reactor，用\"Dispatch Event\"，突出事件分发的语义。其他都没问题了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Dispatch Event"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部调整完毕。最终流程：Aggregate存储事件到Event Store，Event Store分发事件给Reactor，Reactor推送任务到Queue，Queue Worker处理任务并执行Side Effect，最后根据成功或失败分别标记完成或重试。",
